{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"2f40f11553","title":"大字报——还我自由","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"16e85e50ae","index":0,"year":1957,"month":6,"day":null,"articleId":"2f40f11553"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"1f125bc955","name":"哈尔滨师范学院"},{"id":"271e596498","name":"郭宏韬"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"98837d7561","type":"title","text":"大字报——还我自由","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2f40f11553"},{"id":"e854af22fa","type":"authors","text":"哈尔滨师范学院郭宏韬","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2f40f11553"},{"id":"573d6a46b9","type":"subtitle","text":"（郭宏韬：哈尔滨师范学院中文系一、六班学生）","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2f40f11553"},{"id":"a5e492cb2e","type":"paragraph","text":"朋友们，请你们想一想，如果现在没有自由，被谁剥夺去了？前人曾脱光了臂膀，捏紧拳头，冲向水龙、皮鞭和刺刀，夺得了这一自由，然而今天又为什么丧失了这自由？","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2f40f11553"},{"id":"c8b1dcab95","type":"paragraph","text":"要学文学，学了医；要学工，进了师范，多少青年在为祖国前提的帽子不含着眼泪，为着剥削了自己的自由——理想。","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2f40f11553"},{"id":"de051cc8cd","type":"paragraph","text":"给我们自由吧！不要用我们曾所用过的方法去夺取自由。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2f40f11553"},{"id":"e6e5d253bc","type":"paragraph","text":" 来源：《鸣放言论（三）》（哈尔滨：“学习生活”编辑室编，1957年7月10日）。","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2f40f11553"}],"page":{"id":"139cfb00c0","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2f40f11553","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}